{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_51_03",
  "title": "兵藤雫 3話 ファンサが手厚い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、まだ終わんないの？\nもうだいぶやったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ are we not done yet?\nWe've done a lot already.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "あと、三つだけ、です。サインがほしいのと……\nツーショットを撮りたいのと……一緒に釣りがしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just three more left. I want to get your autograph‚ and…\nI want to take a picture together‚ and… I want to go fishing with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "趣味の共有みたいな感じで、釣り、やってみたくて……\n初めてだったら、私が教える、ので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been wanting to try fishing‚ you know‚ like sharing a hobby…\nIf it's your first time‚ I'll teach you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、早く教えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then hurry up and teach me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8366663616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お～！　kanaさん、やる気満々ですね～！\nもうそのまま飛び込んで魚を獲ってきそうな勢いです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! kana-san‚ you're so full of energy!\nYou look like you're about to jump in and catch a fish!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10327.618980399997,
          "startTime": 41.9276189804
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "どんな勢いだよ\n早く終わらせて帰りたいだけだっての",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What energy?\nI just want to finish this quickly and go home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0609523137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、これが釣り竿ね\n糸に、釣り針……あとは餌があればいいってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ so this is a fishing rod.\nA line‚ a hook… And all you need is bait?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2609528224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、やっぱりkanaさんって優しいね……！\nなんだかんだ、ちゃんとやってくれるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ kana-san is so kind after all…!\nShe's doing it properly‚ no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ねー、教えてくれるんじゃないの！？\n早くしてよ、スタッフさん達待たせてんだからさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ aren't you supposed to be teaching me!?\nHurry up‚ you're making the staff wait~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2159641902,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10484.035809700003,
          "startTime": 76.6999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！　あ、これが餌の箱かな？\nkanaさんに持って行くね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay~! Ah‚ is this the bait box?\nI'll take it to kana-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "（……もしかしたら、企画、気に入らなかったかなって）\n（心配だったけど……NGなしで全部やってくれる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Maybe she didn't like the plan?）\n（I was worried… but she's doing everything without saying no…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3219493788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんって、やっぱり凄い……）\n（一緒にお仕事して、ますますリスペクト……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（kana-san is‚ truly amazing…）\n（Working with her makes me respect her even more…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9469619433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、私も準備……って、あれ……そういえば……\n今日用意した餌って……。さ、さくらちゃ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I'll get ready‚ too… Oh‚ wait… Come to think of it…\nThe bait I prepared today… Sa-Sakura-chan――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2469619433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、これが餌みたいです！\n今、箱を開けますね～！　それっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san‚ it looks like this is the bait!\nI'm opening the box now~! Ta-da!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5457.4493843999935,
          "startTime": 108.7201458335
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "ぎいやあああああああああああああああああああ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7749865771,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3154.2650619000055,
          "startTime": 112.929251639
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "虫が苦手な人は……注意、して……\nって、言おうと思ったんだけど……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was going to say… \"People who don't like bugs… be careful…\"\n…But I didn't get the chance…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9292551994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "無理無理無理無理無理、毛虫無理いいいい！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no no no no‚ I hate caterpillars!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9024036647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "か、kanaさん、落ち着いて……！\n後ろ、海――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ka-kana-san‚ calm down…!\nBehind you‚ the ocean――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6959167798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9312264842,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1031.358488099997,
          "startTime": 127.9625849723
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1031.358488099997,
          "startTime": 127.9625849723
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1031.358488099997,
          "startTime": 127.9625849723
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさーーーーーーーーん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-saaaaaaaaaaaan!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7181637168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.1348283489
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.1348283489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、餌の説明、最初にすれば良かった……\n見た目のインパクトが凄いから、気をつけてって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ I should have explained about the bait first…\n…That it's got a pretty impactful appearance‚ so be careful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3625819205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.5214966655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ここまで撮れ高があったおかげで、企画はこれで\n終了みたいです。kanaさん、お疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ thanks to all the footage we got‚ this is the end of the project.\nIt seems. kana-san‚ good work today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5468.616882800006,
          "startTime": 154.9352835495
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2975284617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "帰る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2975284617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3804.8854648999964,
          "startTime": 158.1024139266
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5690805932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん……？\nあ……待って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san…?\nAh… Just a moment…!",
        "id": ""
      },
