      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……あ、あの……\n一杯振り回しちゃって、ごめんなさい……",
