      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとにな！！　サニピのノリ、マジで訳分かんないし\nおまけに海に落ちてずぶ濡れだし。最悪なんですけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously!! I don't get the Sunny Peace vibe at all‚\nAnd on top of that‚ I fell into the ocean and got soaked. This is the worst!",
        "id": ""
