      "startTime": 179.5019939581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……楽しくて、ついはしゃいじゃって……\n推しのkanaさんと、一緒だったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… I was having so much fun‚ I got carried away…\nI was with my bias‚ kana-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.8353272914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あんた、kanaの性格知っててよく推しとか言えるね\n本当にファンな訳？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know kana's personality‚ and you can still call her your bias?\nAre you really a fan?",
